metadata.name: Vinyl Fish Club Membership NFT - Chef Series - 1 #1
metadata.description:
This NFT represents your ownership of membership to our private dining Vinyl Fish Club.

As a VFC member, you will have access to members only events, members dining menu, rare Japanese whiskey & sake tasting invitations, private room (DISUKO-GU), celebrity chef Omakase events, concierge reservation email and more.

Purchase is based on a first come, first serve basis.

As a member, you are entitled to bring a guest (non-token holder) to accompany  you.

All food & beverage costs are paid at time of visit and are not included in the token price.

This token is also an original rare collectible by Miguel Paredes that lives on the Ethereum blockchain.

*All membership benefits are subject to change at the discretion of the venue.
